  "contentHtml": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:43px;line-height:40px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">根</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">据《</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">关于开展</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">“2024年儿童中医药知识启蒙作品征集活动”的通知</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">》</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">要求</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">经单位推荐，</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">李亚真老师指导的</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">《</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">岐黄童康小妙招</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">》（</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">团队成员：赖俊如、陈隆杰、张云涛、张君英</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">）</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">申报中国中医药出版社</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">“</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">2024年儿童中医药知识启蒙</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">作品</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">征集</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">活动</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">”。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">现予公示</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">公示时间：</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">2024年</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\">23</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">日</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\">-</span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;font-size: